rovides a snapshot of the wealth of the village. The asset ";			overviewText += "worth is calculated by multiplying the amount of a given asset by the ";			overviewText += "price that the market would buy that asset for. The value of all non-cash ";			overviewText += "assets are then added together to produce the value here.";			sendNotification(ApplicationFacade.DISPLAY_INFO_TEXT, overviewText);		}	}	}